Metadata Published: {"name": "COVID-19 Community Profile Report - County-Level", "description": "The Community Profile Report (CPR) \u2013 County-Level is generated by the Data Strategy and Execution Workgroup in the Joint Coordination Cell, under the White House COVID-19 Team.
